## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and publications up to October 2023. The perspectives provided may not fully capture the nuances of youth voting behavior across different regions and demographics. Additionally, the rapidly changing political landscape means that new factors influencing youth voting may have emerged since the publication of the sources used in this report.